description: This old English phrase has been passed down through generations of both cultured (and un-cultured) British people. It is high time Alexa also benefitted from this knowledge. Simply ask "Alexa, ask how many beans make five?" No need for an account or special hardware.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask how many beans make five
Alexa, ask how many beans make six
Alexa, ask how many beans make one
name: beans5
shortDescription: This skill is an absolute must have for anybody who is unsure how many beans make five. An old English phrase passed down through generations of cultured Brits.
